{
  "stem": "7069.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we, out of the big garage, or the big barn out there, there were dismantled parts of a beautiful, white lacquered barrack that we had to bring out into the camp, assemble it-- with red shutters, with a beautiful shiny red roof.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It looked like a little building now out of the fairy tale.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it was the nursery.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Small children out of the camp would be dressed, well-bathed, and dressed well, and would be put into this thing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The shelves were full with all kinds of children toys and books.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It happened to be that the Danish delegation came to it-- and before, the Red Cross was the same thing, by the way.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Eventually the Danish delegation that came through happened to be around lunchtime.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The most wonderful food was served to the kids.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The kids had dessert and chocolates.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the kids were prompted to say, in front of this delegation, and of course the Nazi dignitaries with them, oh, to, to the nurses that were dressed in white uniforms, oh, Miss So-and-So, can, can I, can I have another piece of chocolate, please?",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Go right over there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They're in the shelf.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Go, take whatever you want.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you saw this?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Taken in the-- that's what we built up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so-- and on the, on the same corner of the marketplace, there was-- we had to create, we had to take out the tables like a French outdoor cafe scene.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was little round tables with those little wrought iron chairs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There they selected special, fairly good-looking, older folks yet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they put them onto those places.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the corner was made out like a restaurant, building corner.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "These people set out there.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
